<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/nationalreview/15july96/week.html 204.71.237.79 19970209234052 text/html 10272
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 23:41:38 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 30-Jun-96 22:33:35 GMT
