http://www.empower.org:80/nationalreview/31dec95/rusty.htm 204.71.237.79 19970209235152 text/html 4603
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 23:52:39 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 27-Dec-95 15:56:22 GMT
Content-length: 4417
Content-type: text/html
