http://www.empower.org:80/nationalreview/14aug95/cigar.htm 204.71.237.79 19970209235933 text/html 7575
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 00:00:15 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:45 GMT
Content-length: 7392
